In these days data security in networks is the major problem in world.
Information contents may be textual data or image data. The need of exchanging data  
secretly over unsecure networks promoted the creation of cryptosystems to enable 
receivers to interpret the exchanged information.
There are so many different techniques that should be used to protect  image data 
or text data from unauthorized access. 
Classical encryption and modern techniques which are widely used to solve the 
problem in open networked systems, where information is being received and misused
by facilitating attacks at various levels in the communication.
